<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Manufacturing | DGT</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 80vh;
            background: url('/images/industryManufacturing.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 20px);
            min-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tools {
            background: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .cta a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .card {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Manufacturing</h1>
            <p>Optimizing production processes through AI-powered automation and real-time data insights.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <section class="section">
            <h2>Revolutionizing Manufacturing with AI</h2>
            <p>AI-driven solutions are transforming the manufacturing industry by enhancing operational efficiency, automating production, and improving real-time monitoring. DGT's AI-powered analytics and automation optimize production lines, reduce downtime, and boost productivity.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Key AI-Powered Solutions</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Smart Production Planning</h3>
                    <p>AI-powered demand forecasting and real-time scheduling for optimized production.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Predictive Maintenance</h3>
                    <p>Advanced AI models to predict machinery failures and reduce downtime.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Shop Floor Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Real-time AI analytics to monitor production performance and efficiency.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Supply Chain Optimization</h3>
                    <p>AI-driven logistics and procurement for cost efficiency and reduced lead times.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section tools">
            <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
            <p><strong>Salesforce Manufacturing Cloud</strong> | Celonis | Power BI | CI/CD Tools</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section cta">
            <h2>Drive Manufacturing Excellence with AI</h2>
            <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
